OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FWatch Andrew's story...
OL,8,FA man from who was infected with HIV
OL,9,Fand Hepatitis C when he was just five
OL,10,Fyears old in 1983, says he won't stop
OL,11,Fcampaigning until there is justice and
OL,12,Fcompensation for victims of the
OL,13,FInfected Blood Scandal.
OL,15,FAndrew Evans from Worcester co-founded
OL,16,Fthe Tainted Blood campaign in 2006,
OL,17,Fwhich pushed for the independent
OL,18,Finquiry that was published on Monday
OL,19,F20 May. For 41 years he has campaigned
OL,20,Ffor the truth about the contamination
OL,21,Fscandal.
