OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FAt 13 years old, Andy's mum took him
OL,7,Fon an unexpected drive to the
OL,8,Fcountryside to tell him he had HIV.
OL,9,FIt's likely he had been infected at
OL,10,Fjust five years old when he had Factor
OL,11,FVIII injections for Haemophilia.
OL,13,FFactor VIII was a concentrated blood
OL,14,Fclotting protein touted as a wonder
OL,15,Fdrug to stop internal bleeding and it
OL,16,Fwas easy to mix with water and inject
OL,17,Fwith a syringe. So easy that Andy was
OL,18,Fable to administer it himself when he
OL,19,Fwas just four years old.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/21
