OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FAndy's parents started to hear
OL,7,Fconcerns about the drug potentially
OL,8,Fcarrying HIV but were told by doctors
OL,9,Fto keep giving it to their son.
OL,11,FThey weren't told by doctors until
OL,12,FAndy was ten in 1987 that he had HIV,
OL,13,Fand waited a few years before telling
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FAndy told : "I had to start on
OL,17,Fmedication, which meant there was no
OL,18,Fchoice but to tell me at that point.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/21
