OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"She said, 'Well, it's been in the
OL,7,Ffactory, and you've got it' and she
OL,8,Fstarted crying."
OL,10,FAndy said he felt the need to be
OL,11,Fstrong for his parents: "I was 12 or
OL,12,F13, I was invincible and there was
OL,13,Fnothing that I felt could stop me.
OL,15,F"I said to mum, 'Don't worry, you know
OL,16,FI'll get through this. I'll do what it
OL,17,Ftakes. I'll become a researcher or
OL,18,Fscientist or doctor, and I'll find a
OL,19,Fway to cure it."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/21
