OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FAndy was later told that his HIV
OL,7,Fshould be kept a secret from others
OL,8,Fbecause of how other people with the
OL,9,Fdisease had been treated once people
OL,10,Fknew they had it.
OL,12,FAndy spent the rest of his teenage
OL,13,Fyears getting very sick from toxic,
OL,14,Funpleasant drugs and treatments. His
OL,15,Fweight dropped to dangerously low
OL,16,Flevels and he was often sick at school
OL,17,Fwhich isolated him from others.
OL,19,FAt one point a combination of drugs
OL,20,Fled him to have a stroke, and he had
OL,21,Fto have two hip replacements.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/21
