OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F'My job was to stay alive'
OL,8,FAndy says suffering with AIDS in his
OL,9,Fteenage years was an incredibly
OL,10,Fdifficult ordeal for his family to go
OL,11,Fthrough.JHe told : "In some ways. I
OL,12,Fthink being the person infected and
OL,13,Funwell is much easier than being the
OL,14,Fperson looking after a loved one.
OL,16,F"I was just there to do my job which
OL,17,Fwas to stay alive.
OL,19,F" I can only imagine what my parents
OL,20,Fmust have gone through. For years been
OL,21,Ftold that their son is about to die."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/21
