OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FOnce Andy's condition became more
OL,7,Fmanageable with better treatments
OL,8,Favailable, he began to think about
OL,9,Fwhat he wanted achieve with his life.
OL,11,F"My first goal was to reach the year
OL,12,F2000 because that was the future. And
OL,13,FI thought, if I make it there, that's
OL,14,Fmy ambition complete and I'll
OL,15,Freconsider what life means for me at
OL,16,Fthat point.
OL,18,FAmazingly, I made it at the age of 23.
OL,19,FAnd I thought - well I need to do
OL,20,Fsomething with my life."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/21
