OL,6,F'My purpose was to try and get to the
OL,7,Fbottom of this'
OL,9,FIt wasn't until Andy joined a support
OL,10,Fgroup for haemophiliacs that he began
OL,11,Fto realise he wasn't alone.
OL,13,FHe said: "I started to work with the
OL,14,FMcFarland Trust which was a support
OL,15,Fgroup for people with HIV and
OL,16,Fhaemophilia like myself, who got
OL,17,Ftogether to have a chat, talk about
OL,18,Four similarities, the things that
OL,19,Fwe've been through.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/21
