OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"We talked frankly, which I wasn't
OL,7,Fable to do with anyone before - it was
OL,8,Famazing.
OL,10,F"But also having spoken to those
OL,11,Fpeople, I started to get the idea that
OL,12,Fmaybe what happened to us wasn't just
OL,13,Fsome terrible accident, and that maybe
OL,14,Fdecisions could have been made that
OL,15,Fcould have stopped this from happening
OL,16,Fto us all.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/21
