OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"I started to look into it myself. I
OL,7,Ftalked to other people who had
OL,8,Fcampaigned previously and it confirmed
OL,9,Fmy suspicions that all of this could
OL,10,Fhave been prevented."
OL,12,FAndy soon realised that despite the
OL,13,Fyears of his sickness and treatment,
OL,14,Fhe had been lucky to still be alive,
OL,15,Fwhile hundreds had died from the
OL,16,Fscandal.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/21
