OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"I was one of the lucky ones. I
OL,7,Fmanaged to survive until combination
OL,8,Ftherapy came out. But I learned at
OL,9,Fthat point, people had been dropping
OL,10,Flike flies since around 1984.
OL,12,F"I think about half of the people
OL,13,Finfected with HIV at that point had
OL,14,Fdied. I'd made it through, so I
OL,15,Fthought I owe it to them. I started
OL,16,Fthe campaign campaign group Tainted
OL,17,FBlood in 2006."
OL,19,FThe group long campaigned for a public
OL,20,Finquiry to investigate the scandal,
OL,21,Fwhich was first announced in 2017.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/21
