OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FThey're still calling for compensation
OL,7,Ffor victims, a public apology from the
OL,8,FPrime Minister, and for lessons to be
OL,9,Flearned.
OL,11,F'I wasn't told about my Hepatitis C'
OL,13,FAndy didn't find out until he was in
OL,14,Fhis twenties that he was also infected
OL,15,Fwith Hepatitis C, because a doctor let
OL,16,Fit slip by accident during a routine
OL,17,Fappointment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/21
