OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FAndy said: "Hepatitis C exposure was
OL,7,Froughly 90% throughout the entire
OL,8,Fhaemophiliac population who took
OL,9,FFactor VIII in the 1980s.
OL,11,F"One day I went for my haemophilia and
OL,12,FHIV appointment. I was in the
OL,13,Ftreatment room having bloods taken. My
OL,14,Fdoctor popped his head around the door
OL,15,Fand said to the nurse, 'can we check
OL,16,Fhis Hep C genotype?' And that was the
OL,17,Ffirst I'd heard about it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
