OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"It makes me really cross because Hep
OL,7,FC is quite transmissible, it can
OL,8,Fremain alive for a long time outside
OL,9,Fof the body and I hadn't taken any
OL,10,Fparticular care to protect anyone
OL,11,Faround me from it.
OL,13,F"I had been infected for 18 years and
OL,14,Ffor all that time, I could have been
OL,15,Fputting the people around me at risk,
OL,16,Fwhich makes me quite angry."
OL,18,FThe Tainted Blood group came to
OL,19,Frealise this was a trend across the
OL,20,Fcountry.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/21
