OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FAndy continued: "In many cases a
OL,7,Fdiagnosis was deliberately withheld
OL,8,Ffrom them for whatever reason.
OL,10,F"I was a child when it happened to me,
OL,11,Fbut for other people who were in a
OL,12,Fdifferent stage of life - they were
OL,13,Fsexually active. They may even have
OL,14,Fbeen married.
OL,16,F"They could have been easily infecting
OL,17,Ftheir partners with HIV and or
OL,18,FHepatitis C through that time, and
OL,19,Fthey wouldn't have a clue.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/21
