OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"In fact, we know that that did happen
OL,7,Fon several occasions. I think we're
OL,8,Ftalking 40 to 50 people. Partners of
OL,9,Fhaemophiliacs were infected with HIV,
OL,10,Fbecause their partners weren't told
OL,11,Fabout it.
OL,13,F"It is another injustice. It was
OL,14,Fnegligent to expose people around us
OL,15,Fto that danger."
OL,17,F'I want it all to end'
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/21
