OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,FAndy says he wants the long fight for
OL,7,Fjustice to come to a close, so victims
OL,8,Fand their families can get on with
OL,9,Ftheir lives.
OL,11,FHe said: "I want people like myself -
OL,12,Fwho have gone through years of
OL,13,Fsuffering, painful treatments - I want
OL,14,Fthem to be supported.
OL,16,F"I want them to live the rest of their
OL,17,Flives in a meaningful way instead of
OL,18,Fhaving to fight and fight and fight
OL,19,Ffor every little scrap of support from
OL,20,Fthe government.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G18/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
