OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"I want the fight to end. It's been
OL,7,Ffar too long."
OL,9,F"I hope the government ask act swiftly
OL,10,Fto compensate people with as much as
OL,11,Fwould give them a comfortable life for
OL,12,Fthe rest of their lives. I don't think
OL,13,Fthat's too much to ask.
OL,15,F"It has been such an exhausting fight
OL,16,Fevery step of the way to be told no,
OL,17,Fno, no, you can't do that."
OL,19,FAndy admits that 41 years of
OL,20,Fcampaigning has taken its toll on him.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G19/21
