OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"It's exhausting. It's like an unpaid
OL,7,Ffull time job. But it's worse than
OL,8,Fthat, it's the impact that other
OL,9,Fpeople's stories have on you and I get
OL,10,Fphone calls every week from people who
OL,11,Fwant to just talk because they've
OL,12,Fnever spoken to anybody before.
OL,14,F"The way that families were treated
OL,15,Fwhen parents died and they were split
OL,16,Fup and put into different care homes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G20/21
