OL,3,C'41 years after being infected with
OL,4,CHIV, I'm still fighting for justice'
OL,6,F"This is something that is deep, deep
OL,7,Fwithin me and it's not something I can
OL,8,Fever drop until I finally feel that
OL,9,Fthose people have been recognised
OL,10,Fproperly and given the support that
OL,11,Fthey deserve."
